All my configuration files.

Note: 
	* The i3, nvim, and gnome-terminal theme is Tomorrow-Eighties by Chris Kempson and organised using his base-16 scheme:
	https://github.com/chriskempson/base16
	https://github.com/chriskempson/tomorrow-theme

	* Lxde: 
		-Widget theme: made with oomox  
		-Icon theme: Papirus-Dark with orange folders: https://github.com/PapirusDevelopmentTeam/papirus-folders
		-Cursor: Breeze Amber: https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/breeze-amber-cursor-theme/

	* The font is Iosevka SS04 Medium from the AUR: https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/ttf-iosevka

	* Firefox one-line interface: https://www.reddit.com/r/FirefoxCSS/comments/7ignsk/oneline_flat_interface_dark_light/
